message.body: Eden, just want to let you know that Deedy is not doing good and I think it's time. I am taking him this morning at 10:50. So I took off today and dad did too. He's taking us there. I love you!
No. I want to be there!
We have to get ready to go now. Are u able to come?
Eden, he's gone. I'm sorry. He's with HoHo and a field of sparkly balls. I love you!
Chicken, we're ordering chinese for dinner. Don't feel like cooking have a mind splitting headache. What would you like?
Would you eat shrimp and lobster combo dinner and soup?
Doesn't matter. I don't want to think about food right now.
Would you rather have wings and white rice or combo meal
